o Botswana folklore with a run for the ages at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 4.4124267031910366e-11, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 322}, {\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"the ages\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The internet is in raptures.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The internet\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"raptures\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"21-year-old Letsile Tebogo produced the run of his life to claim gold in a much-anticipated 200m event.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"21-year-old Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the run\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"a much-anticipated 200m event\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was the fastest qualifier and the only man to go under 20 seconds in the semi-finals, so he was certainly expected to medal.\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only man\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"20 seconds\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, 100m champion andAmerican superstar Noah Lyleswas the overwhelming favourite to claim gold alongside his compatriot Kenny Bednarek.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100m champion andAmerican superstar\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"Noah\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"the overwhelming favourite\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"his compatriot\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Tebogo ripped up the script and stormed to the line first in 19.46 seconds ahead of Bednarek in 19.62 and Lyles in 19.70.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"the script\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"19.46 seconds\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"Bednarek\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo is the first African man to win this event and it's also the first gold medal in Botswana's history at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 4.4124267031910366e-11, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the first African man\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"the first gold medal\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Touchingly, Tebogo revealed the birthdate of his late mother on his running shoes in the moments after claiming what must have been a truly emotional victory.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"the birthdate\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"his late mother\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"his running shoes\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"the moments\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"a truly emotional victory\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In case you have been living under a rock and missed this staggering sprinting performance, check it out here.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"a rock\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"this staggering sprinting performance\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This man is trending all over the internet and rightly so.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This man\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"the internet\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Letsile Tebogo is the fifth-fastest man over the 200m distance in history.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"the fifth-fastest man\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m distance\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Usain Bolt's mark of 19.19 still sits at the top of the pile, followed by his fellow Jamaican Yohan Blake with 19.26, Lyles who ran 19.31 in Oregon last year and th